Package: ggtreebar
Title: Make Treemap Bar Charts with 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Harry", "Thompson", , "harry@mayesfield.uk", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: 'ggplot2' geoms analogous to 'geom_col()' and 'geom_bar()' that
    allow for treemaps using 'treemapify' nested within each bar segment.
    Also provides geometries for subgroup bordering and text annotation.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
  grid,
  ggplot2,
  treemapify,
  ggfittext,
  dplyr,
  cli
URL: https://github.com/hrryt/ggtreebar, https://hrryt.github.io/ggtreebar/
BugReports: https://github.com/hrryt/ggtreebar/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1.0)
